latestPosts.caption:
~ Sister of Honour ~ 

For my wedding day, I envisioned Manvi’s lehenga as a piece that would harmonize beautifully with my bridal look while keeping it a touch minimal. Crafted from rich, beige raw silk with subtle hints of baby pink, it carried intricate zardosi, Resham, and crystal embroidery. The design felt like the perfect blend — effortlessly complementing my outfit and radiating a quiet elegance that was just right for her.

With Love, 
Sanchi 🤍
